@startuml UC-103_Activity
title UC-103: Process Case Intervention (Activity)

|Field Agent|
start
:Identify Beneficiary Need (Observation/Request);
:Submit Case (Type, Details, Proof);

|Case Worker|
:Authenticate & Validate Scope;
if (Data Complete?) then (yes)
  :Triage: Accept Case;
  :Move to ACTIVE;
else (no)
  :Return for Information / Reject;
  stop
endif

|SCP Core: Workflows|
:Generate Mandatory Intervention Tasks;
:Assign Tasks to Field Agent / Partner;

|Field Agent|
:Receive Task Notification;
:Execute Intervention (e.g., Deliver Food);
:Capture Proof (Signature/Photo);
:Mark Task COMPLETE;

|Case Worker|
:Review Outcome & Proof;
if (Success Criteria Met?) then (yes)
  :Close Case;
  :Archive History;
else (no)
  :Add Follow-up Tasks;
endif

stop
@enduml
